<plot>Delmas Howe is a neoclassical painter with an international reputation. His subject matter often depicts gay men. In his hometown of Truth or Consequeneces New Mexico, fundamentalism is on the rise his work is little known and less accepted. This film is a portrait of both the man and his hometown.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?597379</url></doc>
